      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric inputs sourced from measurements on test articles; uncertainty in inputs propagated to QoI uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Titanium alloy elastic modulus (114 GPa) and yield strength (880 MPa) measured from coupon tensile tests on same material lot as test constructs. Geometry from calibrated CMM measurements of three representative screws. Monte Carlo propagation of input uncertainty (±3% modulus, ±2% geometry) yields QoI uncertainty bands reported in validation comparison. Gradation 3 satisfied."
