      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented mapping between experimental setup parameters and FEA boundary conditions; fixture compliance characterized and incorporated.",
      "rationale": "Test fixture stiffness measured and incorporated into FEA as spring boundary conditions. Displacement measurement locations in FEA match extensometer attachment points in experiment. Applied displacement rate and load cell compliance documented. Full parameter mapping table provided in supporting technical report. Gradation 3 satisfied."
