      "rationale": "E/uval metric computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 for all three QoIs: stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.12), force at 40 mm (1.44). All below pre-specified threshold of 1.96. Percent differences all below 10%. Graphical overlay of FEA prediction intervals and experimental data provided. Gradation 3 satisfied."
