    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; this gap is accepted because the ASTM F1717 standard condition is the sole condition relevant to the regulatory COU and no multi-condition claim is made. Quantitative validation metrics (E/uval < 1.96 for all QoIs; percent differences < 10%) confirm model credibility for the stated COU. Overall credibility assessment: Accepted.",
